{"tid":44454,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[動物台絲打入] 驚唔驚男朋友出trip會偷食","createTime":"2016-12-18T09:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T13:14:29.000Z","uid":6527,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"405a86edb9563f5c57ffa58c65c9599480ea67c6","tid":44454,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"我男朋友今個星期要去歐洲公幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔怕佢會趁我唔係到就去偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢好愛我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平安夜個晚我仲會飛去法國同佢一齊參加Strasbourg既聖誕彌撒 真係諗起都好浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望各位動物台絲打都會搵到個會陪自己過平安夜既男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就唔駛羨慕我有幾幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/175357_338fd8997ac9be6fbbb9fe0721e7c01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F175357_338fd8997ac9be6fbbb9fe0721e7c01a.jpg&h=c6e1674c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"506e21f443daab975e86782c7f993eae18df8cb7","tid":44454,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"偷硬食"},{"pid":"6d353ab7ab0c9ccb5826dc0adee9f2b7f0596a29","tid":44454,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:49:11.000Z","msg":"其實想問樓豬你地gay佬係咪比較專一？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2bb695a7f968fbee17a30bd03c46c49be0b48b","tid":44454,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實想問樓豬你地gay佬係咪比較專一？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要世界上夠多Gay 佬嘅時候<br />\n基本上同普通男人冇分別"},{"pid":"caab5c6adf3903374c478e78b10975ab2445f9f9","