"tid":44454,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:41:01.000Z","msg":"樓主=on9"},{"pid":"78584b3ce901588b2bc8f9dad69bfb9debd4b9a3","tid":44454,"uid":9798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小心呀絲打，啲男人真係好花心咖。<br />\n上次有個男仔約我去六天馬モール行街，點知行到一半，佢突然話依家想去搵佢學姐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n竟然就咁唔理我走左去，嗰時真係激到我扁哂咀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n橙呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我既唯一情敵已經去左外國發展<br />\n想搵都搵佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個世界有啲野話唔埋咖。<br />\n不過見你咁愛你男朋友，就等我比個建議你啦。<br />\n我覺得你最好就早一日飛過去嗰邊陪你男朋友，然後睇實佢。咁就應該帽事咖喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}